sections.Biography:
===Background===
Palla is the daughter of [[Farlen]], the kennelmaster at [[Winterfell]].

===[[Season 2]]===
Palla carries a large pallet of straw through the Great Hall of Winterfell. [[Bran Stark]]'s [[Direwolves|direwolf]] [[Summer]] passes by and she becomes uncomfortable by the direwolf's proximity.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The North Remembers]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

Farlen is defiant when Winterfell is occupied by [[Theon Greyjoy]] and his men. Palla helps him up when he is beaten for his words.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Old Gods and the New]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt; They are both present when [[Theon Greyjoy]] assembles the people after the escape of [[Bran Stark|Bran]] and [[Rickon Stark]] and unveils two charred corpses.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[A Man Without Honor]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
